metadata.name: MEMORY OF A NEVER SEEN FACE
metadata.description:
My work focuses on who we are as humans, our deepest identity, composed of different layers and textures. I am constantly looking for what lies behind... beyond appearances.

This portrait is a digital work composed of different pieces of my traditional paintings that are mixed and reworked digitaly 
 
3000x3000px

Twitter: @Trez-Art
